{"tid":1539892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最驚唔係撤回就收貨","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:31:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:47:57.000Z","uid":55919,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a3f100b3ee0157a1b0bd7d199f6e1e2d0c4a6c1c","tid":1539892,"uid":55919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:31:31.000Z","msg":"最驚係林鄭應承左撤回+獨立調查<br />\n甚至係應承左撤回+獨立調查+撤暴動定性+釋放義士就收貨<br />\n<br />\n根據調查，或者根據鏗鏘集田北辰去訪問和理非<br />\n好多人覺得五大訴求之中只要撤回修例同埋有獨立調查委員會就收貨<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌晒你地，當義士係Condom？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而五大訴求之中，雙真普選應該係最難實現<br />\n習慣左政治失望嘅香港人係咪甘於將個波再次抛畀下一代<br />\n自己就安享其成？<br />\n我話畀你地聽，一日無真普選，過去咁多年嘅問題只會再次出現<br />\n下次可能變成社會評分，或者明日大愚<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以應承自己<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"55b3af6d2135f241ccb57541efc2307dba27e50a","tid":1539892,"uid":55919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:32:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e314db477ac455d2437dc7efec0a49aa800a018","tid":1539892,"uid":55919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:33:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ed280fec09351a2f47235bdd0506370cc4876ad","tid":1539892,"uid":34088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521358e4761036e77685c8f596f85978660284fb","tid":1539892,"uid":55919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b13759426c16ad7df87829b7720e5a3416d3ece","tid":1539892,"uid":55919,"like":0,"dis